    "item_group.cosmopolitan.tab": "Cosmopolitan",
    "jei.cosmopolitan.berry_syrup_bottle.desc": "Depending on the ingredients used to craft the syrup, it can carry one of five flavors: sour, sweet, bitter, spicy, or strange. These flavors can modify the user's existing status effects, alter their duration, and grant additional effects.",
    "jei.cosmopolitan.blisterberry_popsicle_double.desc": "The player can share this type of popsicle with most creatures they meet.",
    "jei.cosmopolitan.boilberry.desc": "These nether-dwelling parasitic plants only have a chance to drop when player kill living entities in specific biomes. Boilberries are found in the Crimson Forest, while Spinalberries appear in the Warped Forest.",
    "jei.cosmopolitan.category.tub_extract": "Tub Extracting",
    "jei.cosmopolitan.category.tub_inject": "Tub Injecting",
    "jei.cosmopolitan.condensed_milk_bucket.desc": "Condensed milk can be used in crafting recipes in place of milk; foods crafted with it will be slightly faster to consume.",
    "jei.cosmopolitan.cream_bucket.desc": "Cream can be used in crafting recipes in place of milk; foods crafted with it will restore extra hunger points.",
    "jei.cosmopolitan.fiddlehead.desc": "Fiddlehead can be dropped when breaking fern or large fern.",
    "jei.cosmopolitan.frozen_dessert_tub.desc": "Frozen Dessert Tubs are a type of specialised block used for crafting and storing frozen dessert. Firstly, pour milk into the tub and add sugar to begin the transformation into condensed milk. Once the tub is closed, the condensed milk will gradually turn into cream. Place an ice or snow block nearby, add flavor ingredients to the cream, and you will have a tub of ice cream.",
    "jei.cosmopolitan.funguis_bottle.desc": "Use a glass bottle on a Shroomlight can extract its sap; an exhausted Shroomlight takes some time to recover.",
    "jei.cosmopolitan.gulime.desc": "A kind of edible golem that can split into 4 small, edible pieces after eating. It will slowly restore if the player has more than 4 pieces in their inventory and might change its form if the restore takes place in some specific biomes.",
